      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery exhibits significant wear in high-traffic areas. While it runs and drives, it will likely need some minor suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to maintain its performance. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
